[color=#00FF00][b]Introduction[/b][/color]
\"The Tired Vampire\" is a tavern located on the shores of lake Ilinalta. It is widely known as a home to the horde of adventurers eating and drinking foolhardily while not questing recklessly.

[b]Features:[/b]
- one huge \"The Tired Vampire\" interior and a small \"The Tired Vampire, Stables\" interior;
- 27 new NPCs with individual behaviour;
- 12 unique scenes;
- 38 conversations;
- a rentable room in the basement;
- a room for sale;
- new potions, food and recipes.

[color=#00FF00][b]Installation[/b][/color]
Extract [color=#FFFF00]TheTiredVampire.bsa[/color], [color=#FFFF00]TheTiredVampire.esm[/color] and [color=#FFFF00]TheTiredVampireScenes.esp[/color] from this archive to the \"Skyrim\\Data\" folder. You should plug in both esm-file and esp-file.

[color=#FF0000][b]Requirements[/b][/color]
Skyrim patched to at least 1.8

[color=#00FF00][b]Credits and thanks[/b][/color]
